cs.CY, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.ED, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the quality of OpenCourseWare (OCW), which is related to computer science education (cs.ED) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The assessment of quality is based on use case scenarios, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.DL). Additionally, the paper discusses the fitness for use of OCW, which is related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
